synopsis: In the 1960s, the city of Alvarenga and the region were stolen by these bull thieves, who scared anyone, but a man promises to bring peace back to the city of Alvarenga and put an end to these evildoers.
Blaire, Mitch, Jess, Adam, Ken and Val are in a chat room when they are surprised by the arrival of a user known only as "Billie227". Thinking that this is just a problem...
